    <p><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l7' data-llen='155:181'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '004-1a' );" name="004-1a" class="pb">[004-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='181:189'>欽定四庫全書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='189:210'>　禹貢長箋卷四　　　　　　吳江朱鶴齡撰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='210:219'>海岱及淮惟徐州</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='219:249'>　爾雅濟東曰徐州<span class='krp-note'>郭璞註自/濟東至海</span>孔傳東至海北至岱南</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='249:272'>　及淮蔡傳徐州之域西不言濟者岱之陽濟東為徐</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='272:295'>　岱之北濟東為青言濟不足以辨故畧之爾雅濟東</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='295:318'>　曰徐州者商無青并青于徐也周禮正東曰青州者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='318:341'>　周無徐并徐于青也林氏之竒曰一州之境必有四</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='341:367'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '004-1b' );" name="004-1b" class="pb">[004-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='367:390'>　至七州皆有二至盖以隣州互見此獨識其三邊者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='390:413'>　嫌同于青揚　熊氏禾曰徐州沂泗諸水在其前冀</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='413:436'>　東兖豫之地皆可接引而在懐抱拱揖之内亦東方</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='436:459'>　一形勝也徐即魯境地連淮海東夷其俗有二曲阜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='459:482'>　沂泗則文雅禮義之邦而彭城則其俗雄傑鷙悍淮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='482:516'>　夷徐戎皆在其地<span class='krp-note'>文頴曰彭城故東楚也/項羽都之謂之西楚</span>愚按禹時</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='516:539'>　淮北為徐州淮南為揚州周淮北為青州春秋時淮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='539:562'>　北為魯為齊為宋南為吳故晉欲通吳必假道宋之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='562:588'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '004-2a' );" name="004-2a" class="pb">[004-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='588:611'>　彭城後楚破越東侵泗上盡取故吳地而淮南地皆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='611:634'>　為楚矣<span class='krp-note'>晉分淮北為北徐/州淮南為南徐州</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='634:661'>　班固配十二次自奎五度至胃六度為降婁之次<span class='krp-note'>費/直</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='661:701'>　<span class='krp-note'>起奎六度蔡邕起奎八/度爾雅降婁奎婁也</span>于辰在戍魯之分野<span class='krp-note'>左傳昭/七年四</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='701:746'>　<span class='krp-note'>月日食于豕韋之末降婁之初士文伯以為魯衛之/惡衛豕韋也魯降婁也周四月今二月日在降婁</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='746:789'>　屬徐州<span class='krp-note'>春秋元命苞天氐星主司弓弩流為徐州别/為魯國廣雅北斗七星四為權權為徐揚州</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='789:812'>　晉天文志奎婁胃魯徐州東海入奎一度瑯琊入奎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='812:835'>　六度髙宻入婁一度城陽入婁九度膠東入胃一度</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='835:861'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '004-2b' );" name="004-2b" class="pb">[004-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='861:884'>　詩譜魯封域在禹貢徐州大野蒙羽之野宋封域在</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='884:907'>　徐州泗濵西及豫州孟豬之野通典徐州魯其分野</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='907:930'>　兼得宋齊吳之交秦置郡此為泗水瑯琊之西境薛</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='930:953'>　郡漢又加置東海郡武帝置十三州復以其地為徐</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='953:976'>　州後漢因之漢地理志魯地東至東海南有泗水至</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='976:1003'>　淮得臨淮之下相睢陵僮取慮<span class='krp-note'>音趨/閭</span>皆魯分地狹民</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='1003:1026'>　衆頗有桑麻之業無林澤之饒宋地今之沛梁楚山</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='1026:1056'>　陽濟隂東平及東郡之須昌夀張皆宋分<span class='krp-note'>内梁國應/入豫州志</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='1056:1082'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '004-3a' );" name="004-3a" class="pb">[004-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='1082:1117'>　<span class='krp-note'>尺云東平須昌夀張皆/在濟東屬魯非宋地也</span>濟隂定陶詩風曹國也宋至</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='1117:1140'>　景公滅曹後五世亦為齊楚魏所滅齊得其濟隂東</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='1140:1179'>　平楚得其沛<span class='krp-note'>史記自鴻溝以東芒碭以北屬鉅/野此梁宋也陶睢陽亦一都㑹也</span>後漢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='1179:1207'>　郡國志徐州刺史<span class='krp-note'>治剡今/剡城</span>部郡國五東海瑯琊彭城</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='1207:1236'>　廣陵下邳通考漢時為東海臨淮<span class='krp-note'>章帝併/入下邳</span>山陽魯郡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='1236:1274'>　而瑯琊郡<span class='krp-note'>南境/是</span>泰山郡<span class='krp-note'>南境/是</span>沛郡<span class='krp-note'>東境是秦/故泗水郡</span>附焉國</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='1274:1303'>　則楚泗水<span class='krp-note'>武帝分東/海郡置</span>唐地理志河南道古徐州域宋</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='1303:1353'>　<span class='krp-note'>碭山單/父是</span>徐<span class='krp-note'>彭/城</span>宿<span class='krp-note'>析徐泗/二州置</span>鄆<span class='krp-note'>東/平</span>曹<span class='krp-note'>濟/隂</span>為大火分兖<span class='krp-note'>魯/郡</span>海</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='1353:1379'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '004-3b' );" name="004-3b" class="pb">[004-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='1379:1426'>　<span class='krp-note'>東/海</span>沂<span class='krp-note'>瑯/琊</span>泗<span class='krp-note'>臨淮本/下邳郡</span>為降婁分濠<span class='krp-note'>鍾/離</span>為星紀分<span class='krp-note'>内宋曹/二州通</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1426:1461'>　<span class='krp-note'>典入豫州鄆州通典入/兖州濠州通典入揚州</span>宋史京東東路則沂州淮陽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1461:1492'>　軍京西西路則襲慶<span class='krp-note'>本兖/州</span>東平<span class='krp-note'>本鄆/州</span>二府徐單二州</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1492:1520'>　淮南東路則宿海泗三州漣水軍<span class='krp-note'>今安/東縣</span>明一統志古</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1520:1558'>　徐州為今南直𨽻徐州<span class='krp-note'>春秋宋地戰國屬楚秦屬泗/水郡漢改沛郡又分立楚國</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1558:1603'>　<span class='krp-note'>置徐州隋為彭城郡唐置武寧軍節度元屬歸徳/府其地東接齊魯南通冮准西控梁宋歴代重鎮</span>淮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='1603:1647'>　安府<span class='krp-note'>春秋屬呉後屬越戰國屬楚秦屬九江郡漢屬/臨准郡及廣陵國東漢屬廣陵郡下邳國晉分</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='1647:1686'>　<span class='krp-note'>廣陵置山陽郡隋唐曰楚州南宋與/金為界其地控山阻海江准安衝</span>則徐揚二州域</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='1686:1712'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '004-4a' );" name="004-4a" class="pb">[004-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='1712:1750'>　<span class='krp-note'>清河安樂㭄源沭陽海州贑榆/邳州宿遷睢寧在准北屬徐州</span>山東兖州府則兖徐</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='1750:1793'>　二州域<span class='krp-note'>嵫陽曲阜寧陽鄒縣泗水滕縣城武嶧縣金/鄉魚臺單縣濟寧州嘉祥鉅野鄆城曹州曹</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='1793:1839'>　<span class='krp-note'>縣定陶沂州郯城費縣屬徐州按菏澤在豫州詩譜/曹國在雷夏菏澤之野則曹縣定陶等地應為兖豫</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='1839:1882'>　<span class='krp-note'>二州之域鄭端簡云曹州南境是徐州鄭又以青/州府之莒州沂水日照安丘諸城蒙隂屬徐州</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='1882:1905'>　于慎行曰余覽古圖經北紀諸山負地絡之隂並太</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='1905:1928'>　行王屋東踰常山至醫無閭而止南紀諸山負地絡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='1928:1951'>　之陽連桐栢熊耳入于甌越江淮河濟東下如建瓴</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='1951:1974'>　矣岱宗獨立海上西向而揖羣山汶洸沂泗出其支</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='1974:2000'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '004-4b' );" name="004-4b" class="pb">[004-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='2000:2023'>　麓旋之如帶以入于海其狀若負扆云徃河流燕齊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='2023:2046'>　間由岱之北挾濟入海今徙徐方顧反出岱岳南挾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='2046:2069'>　淮入海斯地道所由變遷也　陳繼儒曰唐一行云</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='2069:2092'>　天下盡于南北兩戒北有黄河南有長江夾中間大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='2092:2115'>　地曰中條中條之西為豐鎬上應太微垣為天下之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='2115:2138'>　至險豐鎬而東至洛邑上應紫微垣為天下之至中</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='2138:2161'>　文武既都之其中條黄河長江夾至盡處忽泰山插</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='2161:2184'>　天截水西向其左為河濟入海之道其右為江淮入</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='2184:2210'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '004-5a' );" name="004-5a" class="pb">[004-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='2210:2233'>　海之道東魯政在江河夾流中周公又分封于此盖</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='2233:2256'>　中條以豐鎬為首洛陽為腹青徐為尾而周公曉暢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='2256:2280'>　地脉都收拾一家厥後齊先滅魯後亡固見地脉𢎞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='2280:2303'>　逺又生孔顔諸聖賢為文教主非果中條盡龍何以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='2303:2326'>　有此　愚按徐州邊海地在安東贑榆之間不甚延</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='2326:2350'>　長而汴睢汶泗諸水合流其境乃運道襟喉彭城𫝑</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='2350:2373'>　控南北尤兵家攻守之地章俊卿曰禹别九州其道</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='2373:2402'>　里廣狹全不相侔濟河<span class='krp-note'>兖/</span>淮岱<span class='krp-note'>徐/</span>相去不能千里荆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='2402:2428'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '004-5b' );" name="004-5b" class="pb">[004-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l89' data-llen='2428:2460'>　河<span class='krp-note'>豫/</span>千里而嬴海岱<span class='krp-note'>青/</span>千里而縮荆山衡陽<span class='krp-note'>荆/</span>二千</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='2460:2489'>　里東海西河<span class='krp-note'>冀/</span>二千里夀春之淮潮陽之海<span class='krp-note'>揚/</span>相去</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='2489:2515'>　且五千里龍門之黄河燉煌之黒水<span class='krp-note'>雍/</span>相去以四千</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='2515:2540'>　里至華陽之黒水<span class='krp-note'>梁/</span>窮數千里而未知所經是廣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='2540:2563'>　狹之殊也或謂九州之内品别墳壤故道里無得而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l94' data-llen='2563:2592'>　均然荆河淮濟之間<span class='krp-note'>兖徐豫/三州境</span>至不能當淮海一州之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l95' data-llen='2592:2615'>　半使三州壤别難併揚州之大獨不可得而釐耶盖</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l96' data-llen='2615:2638'>　九州之制實倣井田之法王圻居内八州環拱是同</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l97' data-llen='2638:2664'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '004-6a' );" name="004-6a" class="pb">[004-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l98' data-llen='2664:2687'>　養公田之義也故區别境壤不因土宇之大小惟據</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l99' data-llen='2687:2710'>　民田之多寡而均之耳如荆河淮濟之間百舎坦夷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l100' data-llen='2710:2733'>　萬頃一瞬而又當中原要區民力修地利盡故徐兖</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l101' data-llen='2733:2764'>　豫境土最狹也至淮漢以南<span class='krp-note'>揚/荆</span>函劔以西<span class='krp-note'>雍/梁</span>江湖環</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l102' data-llen='2764:2787'>　流闗嶺重複又僻在遐陬濶踈稼政平地盖寡闢田</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l103' data-llen='2787:2810'>　甚難故雍梁最遼濶也西漢去古未逺方其極盛天</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l104' data-llen='2810:2833'>　下户口千二百餘萬徐兖豫當五百五十萬而荆揚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l105' data-llen='2833:2856'>　雍梁四州當三百萬户青冀二州當三百五十萬户</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l106' data-llen='2856:2882'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '004-6b' );" name="004-6b" class="pb">[004-6b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='2882:2905'>　夫民非穀不生穀非民不殖推其戸口之數足以見</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l108' data-llen='2905:2928'>　田疇之多寡九州之别惟民田是均斷可識矣愚按</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l109' data-llen='2928:2951'>　古時封建其疆域道里之數亦當以井田為準如周</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l110' data-llen='2951:2974'>　公封魯孟子云百里明堂位云七百里所謂百里盖</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l111' data-llen='2974:3003'>　指鄼鄙郊遂之地可建畮出賦者而言<span class='krp-note'>如後世所/云實封</span>魯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l112' data-llen='3003:3026'>　地在泰山之陽徂徠梁父諸山皆居封域濟河環之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l113' data-llen='3026:3049'>　其井甸所出固不能越百里而加嬴也若明堂位之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l114' data-llen='3049:3072'>　七百里則包丘陵阪險及附庸閒田在内王制名山</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l115' data-llen='3072:3098'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '004-7a' );" name="004-7a" class="pb">[004-7a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l116' data-llen='3098:3121'>　大川不以封而又有閒田以眡列侯之功罪而予奪</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l117' data-llen='3121:3144'>　之孟子所謂慶以地讓以地者是也然其法止可行</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l118' data-llen='3144:3167'>　于中原博衍之區至于交益甌閩地皆崇山巨浸則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l119' data-llen='3167:3190'>　載師所不能詳此禹服五千里之外先王半棄之而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l120' data-llen='3190:3198'>　為夷貊也歟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l121' data-llen='3198:3204'>淮沂其乂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l122' data-llen='3204:3227'>　曾氏曰淮源出豫至徐揚之間始大汎濫為患尤在</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l123' data-llen='3227:3263'>　于徐故淮之治于此記之<span class='krp-note'>圖經淮河在淮安府治西/南五里自泗州龜山東北</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l124' data-llen='3263:3289'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '004-7b' );" name="004-7b" class="pb">[004-7b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l125' data-llen='3289:3325'>　<span class='krp-note'>流與汴河合/東北入海</span>漢地理志沂水出泰山郡盖縣<span class='krp-note'>一統志/盖城在</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l126' data-llen='3325:3362'>　<span class='krp-note'>青州府沂水縣/西北七十里</span>臨樂山南至下邳<span class='krp-note'>今淮安/府邳州</span>入泗過郡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l127' data-llen='3362:3391'>　三<span class='krp-note'>泰山瑯/琊東海</span>行六百里水經注沂水出泰山盖縣艾山</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l128' data-llen='3391:3435'>　<span class='krp-note'>兖州府志沂河出青州府蒙縣西北一百二十里/艾山水經盖縣艾山即此南流至沂水縣城西</span>水</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l129' data-llen='3435:3459'>　有二源南源所導謂之柞泉北水所𤼵謂之魚窮泉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l130' data-llen='3459:3488'>　俱東南流合為一又東南逕東莞<span class='krp-note'>今青州府/沂水縣</span>西與小</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l131' data-llen='3488:3526'>　沂水合<span class='krp-note'>小沂水出黄孤山西/南流逕東莞注沂</span>又東南逕蒙隂<span class='krp-note'>今屬青/州府</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l132' data-llen='3526:3557'>　北與□崮水<span class='krp-note'>注見青州所謂/入沂之水也</span>合又南過下邳縣西南</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l133' data-llen='3557:3583'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '004-8a' );" name="004-8a" class="pb">[004-8a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l134' data-llen='3583:3606'>　入于泗齊乗鄭康成謂沂水出沂山今蒙縣東北地</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l135' data-llen='3606:3629'>　名南河川小阜下有狗泉此沂源也東南逕馬頭固</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l136' data-llen='3629:3652'>　有泉東流與之合北望沂山五十里殊無别源疑沂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l137' data-llen='3652:3680'>　山水原古流今竭耳沂水南流至沂州<span class='krp-note'>今屬兖/州府</span>城東</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l138' data-llen='3680:3715'>　又南分流入三十六穴湖東通沭<span class='krp-note'>音/術</span>水<span class='krp-note'>沭水南至沭/陽縣又名漣</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l139' data-llen='3715:3754'>　<span class='krp-note'>水地理志沭水出瑯琊東莞縣南/至下邳入泗水經過都陽縣入沂</span>愚按水經注引鄭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l140' data-llen='3754:3778'>　𤣥説沂水出沂山亦云臨樂山寰宇記艾山一名臨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l141' data-llen='3778:3801'>　樂山名雖不同本一山也一統志云艾山在邳州北</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l142' data-llen='3801:3827'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '004-8b' );" name="004-8b" class="pb">[004-8b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l143' data-llen='3827:3850'>　百餘里接沂水縣界沂水所出又云沂水出沂水縣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l144' data-llen='3850:3873'>　西北雕厓山流經本縣南二里豈雕厓即艾山别名</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l145' data-llen='3873:3896'>　歟康成所云沂山特謂沂水所出之山耳而齊乘乃</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l146' data-llen='3896:3919'>　求之臨朐縣南之沂山故疑沂山水源今竭實未必</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l147' data-llen='3919:3942'>　然也金氏履祥曰徐之水以沂名者不一其出今兖</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l148' data-llen='3942:3965'>　州泗水縣尼丘山過魯城南入泗者曾㸃浴沂之沂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l149' data-llen='3965:3988'>　也今海州沭陽縣有沂河口周禮沂沭之沂也出沂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l150' data-llen='3988:4016'>　州新泰縣<span class='krp-note'>今沂/水縣</span>艾山西南入泗者最大此禹貢之沂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l151' data-llen='4016:4042'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '004-9a' );" name="004-9a" class="pb">[004-9a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l152' data-llen='4042:4065'>　也按今沂水一出沂水縣艾山會沂蒙諸泉與沂山</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l153' data-llen='4065:4088'>　之汶合流至邳入泗逹淮地志所謂出泰山盖縣者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l154' data-llen='4088:4111'>　是也一出曲阜尼山東南六十里西流至兖城與泗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l155' data-llen='4111:4134'>　合注濟寧水經注所謂出尼丘經雩壇者是也其沭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l156' data-llen='4134:4158'>　陽之沂一統志不載疑即艾山𣲖耳金氏分為三恐</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l157' data-llen='4158:4190'>　非蔡傳徐之水有泗有汶有汴有漷<span class='krp-note'>水經注漷水出/東海合鄉縣西</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l158' data-llen='4190:4222'>　<span class='krp-note'>南至胡陵縣入/泗今在沛縣東</span>而獨以淮沂言者周職方氏青州其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l159' data-llen='4222:4245'>　川淮泗其浸沂沭周之青即禹之徐則徐之川浸固</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l160' data-llen='4245:4271'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '004-9b' );" name="004-9b" class="pb">[004-9b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l161' data-llen='4271:4306'>　莫大于淮沂也<span class='krp-note'>周禮注水流而趨海者曰/川深積而成潤者曰浸</span>　中都志</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l162' data-llen='4306:4337'>　淮水流懐逺縣東南歴荆塗二山硤間<span class='krp-note'>淮出荆山之/左塗山之右</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l163' data-llen='4337:4373'>　乃神禹所鑿<span class='krp-note'>今兩崖石㡾猶存有巨石横/梗若門限毎冬水淺則見</span>梁武帝嘗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l164' data-llen='4373:4384'>　于此立堰以灌夀陽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l165' data-llen='4384:4407'>　徐州之水合于吕梁而入于淮淮水北受泗沂本皆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l166' data-llen='4407:4430'>　清流若黄河入海于天津汴河入海于樂安與淮無</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l167' data-llen='4430:4461'>　與也自沁河<span class='krp-note'>在懐慶府城/北源出沁州</span>决斷黄河黄河决斷汴河</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l168' data-llen='4461:4493'>　從朱僊鎮<span class='krp-note'>在開/封府</span>東潰南經留城<span class='krp-note'>在沛/縣</span>趨徐邳亂洸汴</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l169' data-llen='4493:4520'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '004-10a' );" name="004-10a" class="pb">[004-10a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l170' data-llen='4520:4543'>　直下不復東流乃徑决清河縣西而南入于淮以趨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l171' data-llen='4543:4566'>　海故直謂之黄河非復泗沂之舊清河以東之淮亦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l172' data-llen='4566:4589'>　皆黄流而支河反為主矣至運河之水必頼黄河乃</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l173' data-llen='4589:4613'>　河水西入淮則𫝑分而東流益緩其力不能刷沙闗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l174' data-llen='4613:4637'>　套所在淤積日甚而尾閭㡬于不泄又黄水多𤼵于</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l175' data-llen='4637:4661'>　四五月鳯泗水多𤼵于七八月河長潰淮淮長亦潰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l176' data-llen='4661:4684'>　河此為交蝕之害泗州河身髙于運河丈許自髙趨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l177' data-llen='4684:4708'>　下其𫝑陡激以區區漕渠為鳯泗之歸宿毎崩五壩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l178' data-llen='4708:4735'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '004-10b' );" name="004-10b" class="pb">[004-10b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l179' data-llen='4735:4759'>　掃湖頭嘴諸市而與淮一此為泗河獨𤼵之害倘淮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l180' data-llen='4759:4784'>　黄並𤼵泗沂沁汴諸流横益滔天𫝑不能南越維揚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l181' data-llen='4784:4807'>　之髙以入于江則停泗淹灌于全淮之境所必至也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l182' data-llen='4807:4831'>　愚按古河辨謂河濁淮泗俱清清淮𫝑大可以吞伏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l183' data-llen='4831:4854'>　故下流無閼塞之患黄流之不直趨維揚者以淮水</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l184' data-llen='4854:4885'>　為之障耳沂在淮東與泗合今清河<span class='krp-note'>淮以北水皆清/故謂之清河</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l185' data-llen='4885:4923'>　乃泗水下流經邳州<span class='krp-note'>清河在邳州治西一里許其東/為直河其西為沙河中都志沙</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l186' data-llen='4923:4951'>　<span class='krp-note'>河即/潁水</span>南至清河縣西北三汊河口分大小清河入淮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l187' data-llen='4951:4978'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '004-11a' );" name="004-11a" class="pb">[004-11a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l188' data-llen='4978:4988'>　<span class='krp-note'>見皇/輿考</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l189' data-llen='4988:4994'>蒙羽其藝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l190' data-llen='4994:5022'>　漢地理志蒙山在泰山郡蒙隂縣<span class='krp-note'>今屬青/州府</span>西南林氏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l191' data-llen='5022:5057'>　之竒曰即論語東蒙<span class='krp-note'>邢昺曰顓臾主祭蒙山在/東故曰東蒙一名東山</span>詩奄</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l192' data-llen='5057:5080'>　有龜蒙齊乗蒙山在龜山東二山連屬長八十里漢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l193' data-llen='5080:5114'>　地理志羽山在東海郡祝其縣<span class='krp-note'>今淮安府海州贑榆/縣一統志在贑榆縣</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l194' data-llen='5114:5142'>　<span class='krp-note'>西北八/十里</span>南鯀所殛齊乗今沂州東南百二十里殛鯀</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l195' data-llen='5142:5176'>　山也<span class='krp-note'>一統志登州蓬萊縣/有羽山亦云殛鯀處</span>愚按羽山近海在蒙之東</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l196' data-llen='5176:5203'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '004-11b' );" name="004-11b" class="pb">[004-11b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l197' data-llen='5203:5236'>　前有羽潭左傳鯀化為黄能<span class='krp-note'>音台爾雅/三足鼈</span>入于羽淵<span class='krp-note'>淮/南</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l198' data-llen='5236:5273'>　<span class='krp-note'>子帝使祝融殺之于羽淵拾/遺記鯀治水無績自沈羽淵</span>王樵曰詩藝之荏菽故</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l199' data-llen='5273:5304'>　藝為種<span class='krp-note'>周禮疏樹是植/木藝是黍稷</span>　王氏炎曰先淮後沂先大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l200' data-llen='5304:5327'>　而後小也先蒙後羽先髙而後下也淮沂乂而蒙羽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l201' data-llen='5327:5359'>　可藝事之相因也<span class='krp-note'>其藝言可施功/樹藝與既萟别</span>茅瑞徴曰山之可</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l202' data-llen='5359:5382'>　種萟者衆矣而獨舉徐之蒙羽與梁之岷嶓以例餘</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l203' data-llen='5382:5405'>　州岷嶓江漢所出山最髙大蒙羽非其配也而為淮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l204' data-llen='5405:5428'>　所經意其壤地沃饒畧有同歟經云徐田上中齊乘</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l205' data-llen='5428:5455'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '004-12a' );" name="004-12a" class="pb">[004-12a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l206' data-llen='5455:5478'>　稱沂州東南芙蓉山下有湖溉田數千頃香粳鍾畆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l207' data-llen='5478:5507'>　古稱瑯琊之稻元和志承縣界<span class='krp-note'>今兖州/府嶧縣</span>有陂十三所</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l208' data-llen='5507:5530'>　沂嶧間仰泇承二水溉田青徐水利莫與為匹皆十</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l209' data-llen='5530:5553'>　三陂之遺跡則蒙羽為沃壤可知今近徐諸山彌望</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l210' data-llen='5553:5559'>　荒麓矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l211' data-llen='5559:5572'>大野既豬<span class='krp-note'>豬史/作都</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l212' data-llen='5572:5604'>　漢地理志大野澤在山陽郡鉅野縣<span class='krp-note'>縣以凙名鉅即/大也今屬兖州</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l213' data-llen='5604:5632'>　<span class='krp-note'>府濟/寧州</span>北水經濟水至濟隂郡乗氏縣分為二南為菏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l214' data-llen='5632:5659'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '004-12b' );" name="004-12b" class="pb">[004-12b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l215' data-llen='5659:5686'>　水北為濟瀆酈道元曰一水東南流<span class='krp-note'>菏/澤</span>一水東北流</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l216' data-llen='5686:5728'>　入鉅野澤<span class='krp-note'>濟水㑹濮水自濮陽南入鉅野一統志鉅/野澤在鉅野縣東五里南北三百里東西</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l217' data-llen='5728:5760'>　<span class='krp-note'>一百餘里元末為/黄河所决遂涸</span>何承天曰鉅野廣大南導洙泗北</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l218' data-llen='5760:5784'>　連清濟舊縣故城正在澤中昔西狩𫉬麟于是處也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l219' data-llen='5784:5815'>　<span class='krp-note'>其澤在曲阜/西故云西狩</span>曾氏曰周禮職方河東曰兖州其澤藪</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l220' data-llen='5815:5838'>　曰大野大野為濟之所絶禹時盖在徐之西兖之東</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l221' data-llen='5838:5861'>　也周無徐故專屬兖周必大曰濟水貫兖與徐其在</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l222' data-llen='5861:5884'>　四瀆得天地質信寛徐之氣故大野為爾雅十藪之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l223' data-llen='5884:5911'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '004-13a' );" name="004-13a" class="pb">[004-13a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l224' data-llen='5911:5934'>　首蔡傳水蓄而復流者謂之豬　王樵曰蔡傳謂鄆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l225' data-llen='5934:5957'>　州中都西南有大野陂宋鄆州今東平州即古東原</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l226' data-llen='5957:5985'>　而中都則汶上縣也今南旺湖實在汶上西南<span class='krp-note'>汶水/東南</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l227' data-llen='5985:6024'>　<span class='krp-note'>流至/此分</span>縈廻百五十餘里<span class='krp-note'>河紀南旺湖周百里/蜀山湖周六十五里</span>漕河貫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l228' data-llen='6024:6058'>　乎其中西湖<span class='krp-note'>南/旺</span>廣衍倍于東湖<span class='krp-note'>蜀山湖即/南旺東湖</span>而東湖北</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l229' data-llen='6058:6081'>　接馬踏伍莊坡湖以及安山南接馬塲坡湖以及昭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l230' data-llen='6081:6104'>　陽諸湖綿亘數百里而東原徐鄆諸邑又悉環列于</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l231' data-llen='6104:6127'>　左右與古經志合是南旺湖即古大野無疑愚按漢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l232' data-llen='6127:6154'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '004-13b' );" name="004-13b" class="pb">[004-13b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l233' data-llen='6154:6177'>　武時河决瓠子東南注鉅野通淮泗五代以後河水</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l234' data-llen='6177:6200'>　南徙滙于鉅野王方麓謂即南旺河考河紀云南旺</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l235' data-llen='6200:6223'>　在運河西岸即鉅野澤東畔是鉅又在南旺之西齊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l236' data-llen='6223:6246'>　乗又云鉅野今梁山濼北出為清河盖宋時與濼水</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l237' data-llen='6246:6267'>　滙而為一圍三百餘里自㑹通河開始畫為二</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l238' data-llen='6267:6290'>　考禹時大野既鍾清濟洙泗而成而泗通于淮濟通</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l239' data-llen='6290:6313'>　于汶淮通于沂汶通于洸而泗之上源又自大野而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l240' data-llen='6313:6336'>　通于濟則是大江以北中原諸水縱横交織皆于大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l241' data-llen='6336:6363'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '004-14a' );" name="004-14a" class="pb">[004-14a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l242' data-llen='6363:6386'>　野相連而當時入貢之路若青之浮汶兖之浮濟徐</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l243' data-llen='6386:6409'>　與揚之浮淮泗亦皆大野相闗是大野在古已為貢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l244' data-llen='6409:6436'>　道之要㑹矣明代漕運尤資之設四水櫃曰南旺<span class='krp-note'>在/汶</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l245' data-llen='6436:6481'>　<span class='krp-note'>上/</span>曰安山<span class='krp-note'>在東/平</span>曰馬塲<span class='krp-note'>在濟/寧</span>曰昭陽<span class='krp-note'>在沛/縣</span>各建閘<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0309' title='KR0309' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0309.png'/></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l246' data-llen='6481:6510'>　以時啟閉而南旺分水嶺地最髙所謂水脊<span class='krp-note'>李化龍/曰其地</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l247' data-llen='6510:6554'>　<span class='krp-note'>為安山湖鉅嘉以北諸水注之而出于張秋其/南為南旺湖鉅嘉以北諸水注之而出于魚臺</span>向非</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l248' data-llen='6554:6577'>　南旺㑹通雖開亦枯瀆耳但今者有沙淤盗佃决隄</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l249' data-llen='6577:6600'>　之三患此不獨漕河失利而泰山以西地漸窪下夏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l250' data-llen='6600:6627'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '004-14b' );" name="004-14b" class="pb">[004-14b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l251' data-llen='6627:6651'>　秋水𤼵俱奔注此中宋末嘉祥鉅野曹濮夀張之間</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l252' data-llen='6651:6674'>　遂成巨浸是以有梁山濼之亂今湖外皆民田也若</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l253' data-llen='6674:6691'>　隄防稍廢水将漫衍淹沒可無慮哉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l254' data-llen='6691:6697'>東原厎平</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l255' data-llen='6697:6720'>　孔傳東原致功而平言可耕蔡傳東原漢東平國今</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l256' data-llen='6720:6743'>　之鄆州厎平者水患去而厎于平也後人以其地之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l257' data-llen='6743:6766'>　平故謂東平又按東原在徐之西北而謂之東者以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l258' data-llen='6766:6789'>　在濟東故也漢東平國在景帝亦曰濟東國益知大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l259' data-llen='6789:6816'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '004-15a' );" name="004-15a" class="pb">[004-15a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l260' data-llen='6816:6852'>　野東原所以志濟也<span class='krp-note'>徐無濟濟之分流入大野/而東原在其東故謂志濟</span>晁氏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l261' data-llen='6852:6879'>　以道曰東平自古多水患數徙其城咸平中<span class='krp-note'>宋真/宗</span>又</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l262' data-llen='6879:6902'>　徙城于東南其下濕可知　王氏炎曰大野豬而後</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l263' data-llen='6902:6925'>　東原平亦事之相因也　兖州府志東平州唐天平</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l264' data-llen='6925:6948'>　節度使所治城東地肥饒蘆泉之沃頗宜粳稻其西</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l265' data-llen='6948:6969'>　安山陂澤當汶水下流蓄而不能洩輒成巨浸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l266' data-llen='6969:6996'>厥土赤埴墳草木漸包<span class='krp-note'>埴鄭王讀作熾漸/包古文竹蔪包</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l267' data-llen='6996:7019'>　蔡傳土黏曰埴埴膩也考工記摶埴之工老氏言埏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l268' data-llen='7019:7046'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '004-15b' );" name="004-15b" class="pb">[004-15b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l269' data-llen='7046:7069'>　埴以為噐惟土性黏膩細宻故可搏可埏也漸進長</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l270' data-llen='7069:7108'>　也如易所謂木漸<span class='krp-note'>姚舜牧曰易漸卦有漸進之義若/鴻漸于木非此之解此外又别無</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l271' data-llen='7108:7139'>　<span class='krp-note'>所謂木漸蔡/盖未深考耳</span>言日進于茂而不已也苞樷生也如詩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l272' data-llen='7139:7172'>　所謂如竹苞矣言其樷生而積也<span class='krp-note'>爾雅苞稹也孫炎/曰物樷生曰苞齊</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l273' data-llen='7172:7200'>　<span class='krp-note'>人名/曰稹</span>王樵曰埴土性之美者而又墳起最宜于生物</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l274' data-llen='7200:7208'>　故草木漸包</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l275' data-llen='7208:7219'>厥田惟上中厥賦中中</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l276' data-llen='7219:7242'>　田第二賦第五胡瓉曰土禀冲和之氣故壤為上太</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l277' data-llen='7242:7269'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '004-16a' );" name="004-16a" class="pb">[004-16a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l278' data-llen='7269:7292'>　燥者不凝故墳次之青州墳在壤上者以有斥鹵之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l279' data-llen='7292:7313'>　利豫州土亦壤而先冀者或曰賦逓為上下也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l280' data-llen='7313:7336'>厥貢惟土五色羽畎夏翟嶧陽孤桐泗濵浮磬淮夷蠙</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l281' data-llen='7336:7364'>珠暨魚厥篚𤣥纎縞<span class='krp-note'>翟漢書作狄暨史/記作泉泉古暨字</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l282' data-llen='7364:7387'>　孔傳王者封五色土為社建諸侯則各割其方色土</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l283' data-llen='7387:7424'>　與之使立社<span class='krp-note'>天子火社五文諸侯半之周書/作雒篇受削土于周室即此</span>燾以黄</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l284' data-llen='7424:7458'>　土<span class='krp-note'>覆/也</span>苴以白茅<span class='krp-note'>疏云用白茅/裹土與之</span>茅取其潔黄取王者覆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l285' data-llen='7458:7481'>　四方蔡傳徐州土赤而五色之土亦間有之故制以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l286' data-llen='7481:7508'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '004-16b' );" name="004-16b" class="pb">[004-16b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l287' data-llen='7508:7551'>　為貢<span class='krp-note'>漢郊祀志徐州牧歳貢五色土各一斗一統志/徐州北二十五里有赭土山禹時貢土即此</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l288' data-llen='7551:7585'>　羽畎羽山之谷也夏翟雉具五色<span class='krp-note'>周禮注夏翟總名/其𩔖有六曰翬曰</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l289' data-llen='7585:7627'>　<span class='krp-note'>摇曰□曰甾曰希曰蹲師曠禽經五色備/曰翬亦曰夏翟張華曰雉尾至夏則光鮮</span>其羽中旌</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l290' data-llen='7627:7650'>　旄周禮染人秋染夏染夏者染五色也林氏之竒曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l291' data-llen='7650:7673'>　古之車服噐用以雉為飾者多不獨旌旄漢地理志</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l292' data-llen='7673:7704'>　葛嶧山在東海下邳縣西<span class='krp-note'>一統志在邳州/城西北六里</span>古文以為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l293' data-llen='7704:7739'>　嶧陽又魯國鄒縣北有嶧山<span class='krp-note'>史記正義鄒嶧山在兖/州鄒縣南二十二里鄒</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l294' data-llen='7739:7781'>　<span class='krp-note'>山記鄒山古之嶧山魯穆公改為鄒山今/其地猶多桐樹一統志在鄒縣東南五里</span>郭璞曰嶧</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l295' data-llen='7781:7808'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '004-17a' );" name="004-17a" class="pb">[004-17a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l296' data-llen='7808:7831'>　山純石積搆連屬如繹絲然禹貢作嶧奠其名也魯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l297' data-llen='7831:7854'>　頌作繹取其義也愚按魯頌保有鳬繹遂荒徐宅今</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l298' data-llen='7854:7877'>　鳬山嶧山並在鄒縣南此嶧陽乃鄒嶧山非葛嶧也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l299' data-llen='7877:7900'>　蔡傳孤桐特生之桐其材中琴瑟詩曰梧桐生矣于</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l300' data-llen='7900:7935'>　彼朝陽盖桐以向日為貴也<span class='krp-note'>陸農師曰桐性便濕地/不生于岡詩傳梧桐不</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l301' data-llen='7935:7974'>　<span class='krp-note'>生髙岡太平而後生朝陽以此觀/之生山難得而生孤者尤難得也</span>浮磬石露水濵若</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l302' data-llen='7974:7997'>　浮水然或曰石浮生土中不根著者今下邳有磬石</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l303' data-llen='7997:8034'>　山或以為占取磬之地<span class='krp-note'>括地志泗水至彭城吕梁出/石磬一統志磬石山在邳州</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l304' data-llen='8034:8061'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '004-17b' );" name="004-17b" class="pb">[004-17b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l305' data-llen='8061:8107'>　<span class='krp-note'>城西南八十里與泗水近山有石可為磬又鳯陽靈/璧縣北七十里有山亦出磬石或云禹時泗水當經</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l306' data-llen='8107:8142'>　<span class='krp-note'>流至此茅瑞徴曰泗濵/今泗水縣是磬跡尚存</span>陳氏大猷曰石輕浮可為磬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l307' data-llen='8142:8174'>　者成而貢之磬聲清越取輕浮者良<span class='krp-note'>正義貢石而言/磬者此石宜為</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l308' data-llen='8174:8203'>　<span class='krp-note'>磬猶如/砥礪然</span>淮夷見費誓孔傳作淮夷二水非是正義蠙</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l309' data-llen='8203:8226'>　是蚌之别名蠙出珠遂以為珠名説文淮水出班珠</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l310' data-llen='8226:8260'>　<span class='krp-note'>珠之有聲者今泗州/名蠙城古有蠙珠潭</span>蔡傳珠為服飾魚用祭祀今濠</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l311' data-llen='8260:8291'>　泗楚皆貢淮白魚亦古之遺制歟<span class='krp-note'>一統志淮/水出白魚</span>𤣥赤黒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l312' data-llen='8291:8327'>　色幣<span class='krp-note'>今深紫𩔖/皂者是</span>為衮以祭為端以齋<span class='krp-note'>衣有襦/裳曰端</span>為冠以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l313' data-llen='8327:8354'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '004-18a' );" name="004-18a" class="pb">[004-18a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l314' data-llen='8354:8388'>　居纎縞皆繒名黒經白緯曰纎<span class='krp-note'>孔傳纎細也纎在中/明二物皆當細非是</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l315' data-llen='8388:8418'>　縞白色繒<span class='krp-note'>小爾雅繒之/精者曰縞</span>禮曰及期而大祥素縞麻衣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l316' data-llen='8418:8441'>　中月而禫禫而纎皆去凶即吉之服　徐州制貢大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l317' data-llen='8441:8464'>　畧並供禮樂之用土五色雉羽亦五色物華天寳靈</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l318' data-llen='8464:8487'>　有獨鍾厥後元公啟土于龜蒙夫子領徒于洙泗其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l319' data-llen='8487:8495'>　端已見此矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l320' data-llen='8495:8504'>浮于淮泗逹于河</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l321' data-llen='8504:8533'>　地理志泗水出魯國卞縣<span class='krp-note'>今兖州府/泗水縣</span>西南至山陽方</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l322' data-llen='8533:8560'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '004-18b' );" name="004-18b" class="pb">[004-18b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l323' data-llen='8560:8602'>　與<span class='krp-note'>音方/預</span>縣<span class='krp-note'>今兖州府/魚臺縣</span>入沛<span class='krp-note'>即/泲</span>過郡二<span class='krp-note'>魯國/山陽</span>行五百里</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l324' data-llen='8602:8648'>　<span class='krp-note'>志又云泗水出濟隂乗氏縣東南至臨准睢陵縣入/淮按一統志乗氏城在鉅野西南漢縣也各志皆不</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l325' data-llen='8648:8685'>　<span class='krp-note'>云泗水所出道/元已辨其誤</span>水經注泗水出魯卞縣桃墟<span class='krp-note'>杜預曰/魯國卞</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l326' data-llen='8685:8722'>　<span class='krp-note'>縣東南/有桃墟</span>西北陪尾山<span class='krp-note'>一統志在泗水/縣東五十里</span>石穴吐水五泉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l327' data-llen='8722:8755'>　俱導自卞而合洙水南逕魯城北<span class='krp-note'>從征記洙泗二水/交于魯城東北十</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l328' data-llen='8755:8789'>　<span class='krp-note'>七/里</span>合沂水<span class='krp-note'>此出尼丘/山之沂也</span>又南過方與縣東合菏水又東</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l329' data-llen='8789:8826'>　南逕宿預城<span class='krp-note'>今淮安府/宿遷縣</span>西又東逕角城<span class='krp-note'>晉縣故城在/宿遷縣東南</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l330' data-llen='8826:8849'>　北東南流注于淮王樵曰泗入淮淮泗不與河通而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l331' data-llen='8849:8876'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '004-19a' );" name="004-19a" class="pb">[004-19a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l332' data-llen='8876:8899'>　云逹于河何也盖灉水出于河而入于泗者也由泗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l333' data-llen='8899:8922'>　遡灉由灉遡河此一道也濟入河南出而泗則至大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l334' data-llen='8922:8945'>　野受濟之合者也由泗之上源以遡濟由濟而逹河</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l335' data-llen='8945:8968'>　又一道也西則由灉東則由濟愚按此説本漢許慎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l336' data-llen='8968:8991'>　疏云徐州北接青州既浮淮泗當浮汶入濟以逹于</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l337' data-llen='8991:9014'>　河然考汶泗通流始自近代古時汶北入海泗南入</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l338' data-llen='9014:9037'>　淮二水不相沿注故蔡傳用許氏之説又仁山金氏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l339' data-llen='9037:9060'>　言古文尚書作逹于菏説文引書亦作菏菏澤與濟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l340' data-llen='9060:9087'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '004-19b' );" name="004-19b" class="pb">[004-19b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l341' data-llen='9087:9110'>　相通而泗水上注之徐州之貢自泗逹菏則逹濟可</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l342' data-llen='9110:9133'>　知然八州之貢皆以逹河為至兖州言逹于河故青</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l343' data-llen='9133:9156'>　不言徐州言逹于河故揚不言其義實相因安知古</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l344' data-llen='9156:9179'>　文不有誤耶　蘇傳自淮泗入河必道于汴世謂隋</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l345' data-llen='9179:9202'>　煬帝始通汴入泗疑禹時無此水道按漢書項羽與</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l346' data-llen='9202:9225'>　漢約中分天下割鴻溝以西為漢以東為楚文頴注</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l347' data-llen='9225:9257'>　云于滎陽下引河東南為鴻溝<span class='krp-note'>應劭云鴻溝在滎/陽東南二十里</span>以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l348' data-llen='9257:9280'>　通宋鄭陳蔡曹衛與濟汝淮泗會于楚即今官渡是</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l349' data-llen='9280:9307'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '004-20a' );" name="004-20a" class="pb">[004-20a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l350' data-llen='9307:9331'>　也魏武與𡊮紹相持于官渡乃楚漢分裂之處盖自</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l351' data-llen='9331:9354'>　秦漢以來有之安知非禹跡耶禹貢各州之末皆記</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l352' data-llen='9354:9377'>　入河水道而淮泗獨不能入河帝都所在理不應爾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l353' data-llen='9377:9400'>　意其必開此道以通之其後或為鴻溝或為官渡或</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l354' data-llen='9400:9423'>　為汴上下百餘里間不可必然皆引水而注淮泗也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l355' data-llen='9423:9446'>　故王濬伐吳杜預與之書曰足下既摧其西藩當徑</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l356' data-llen='9446:9469'>　取秣陵自江入淮逾于泗汴泝河而上振旅還都夫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l357' data-llen='9469:9492'>　王濬舟師之盛自古未有而自泗汴入河可以班師</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l358' data-llen='9492:9519'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '004-20b' );" name="004-20b" class="pb">[004-20b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l359' data-llen='9519:9542'>　則汴水之大當不減于今亦足以見秦漢魏晉皆有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l360' data-llen='9542:9565'>　此水道非隋煬剏開也自唐以前汴泗㑹于彭城之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l361' data-llen='9565:9588'>　東北然後東南入淮近嵗汴水直逹于淮不復入泗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l362' data-llen='9588:9633'>　矣<span class='krp-note'>羅泌曰汴渠自古有之晉義熙中劉毅通之以伐/秦始有湍流利漕史謂渠隄自滎陽而東則上疑</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l363' data-llen='9633:9679'>　<span class='krp-note'>其為鴻溝下疑其為官渡有不然者今汴渠自西而/東鴻溝横互南北而官渡直黄河爾鴻溝在今河隂</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l364' data-llen='9679:9711'>　<span class='krp-note'>縣官渡在今中牟/縣俱屬開封府</span>茅瑞徴曰淮在徐之南泗自北而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l365' data-llen='9711:9734'>　南入淮由淮入泗可一航而至但泗不與河通故或</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l366' data-llen='9734:9757'>　由灉或由濟並逆流以上方能逹河今運河亦從淮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l367' data-llen='9757:9784'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '004-21a' );" name="004-21a" class="pb">[004-21a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l368' data-llen='9784:9807'>　合泗而接流㑹通河必經于濟此取道山東者也子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l369' data-llen='9807:9830'>　瞻所指汴水盖自宋都河南一路言之豈所謂汳水</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l370' data-llen='9830:9839'>　由灉入泗者歟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l371' data-llen='9839:9863'>　考近志泗氷四源並𤼵循泗水城北八里合為一西</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l372' data-llen='9863:9892'>　流至曲阜經嵫陽城東五里與沂水雩水合<span class='krp-note'>沂水過/曲阜而</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l373' data-llen='9892:9926'>　<span class='krp-note'>至雩水過鄒縣而至雩/水出曲阜南虎跑泉</span>入金口堰又南流三十里納</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l374' data-llen='9926:9949'>　闕黨諸泉謂之濟河至濟寧州東城下與汶水合入</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l375' data-llen='9949:9986'>　于漕<span class='krp-note'>一統志今泗水至濟寧分流南/流入徐州境北流入㑹通河</span>商輅曰汶泗二</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l376' data-llen='9986:10013'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '004-21b' );" name="004-21b" class="pb">[004-21b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l377' data-llen='10013:10036'>　水分流南北不相通自古浮于汶者自兖北而止浮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l378' data-llen='10036:10059'>　于泗者自兖南而止元時南方貢賦之來至濟寧陸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l379' data-llen='10059:10082'>　行數百里後從濟寧開渠抵安民山復從安民山開</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l380' data-llen='10082:10105'>　渠至臨清乃于兖東築金口堰障泗水西南流兖北</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l381' data-llen='10105:10135'>　築堽城<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0309' title='KR0309' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0309.png'/>障汶水南流而二水悉歸漕渠于是舟艦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l382' data-llen='10135:10158'>　徃來無阻因名㑹通河　丘濬曰漢以來漕路所謂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l383' data-llen='10158:10181'>　汴船不入河者率由蔡河經泗州入淮而吕梁之險</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l384' data-llen='10181:10217'>　<span class='krp-note'>吕梁洪在今徐州城東吕/梁山下昔稱天險今削平</span>未有以之為運道者惟謝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l385' data-llen='10217:10244'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '004-22a' );" name="004-22a" class="pb">[004-22a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l386' data-llen='10244:10268'>　𤣥肥水之役堰吕梁水利漕盖瀦水以暫用耳非通</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l387' data-llen='10268:10291'>　運也宋真宗時趙守倫建議自京東分廣濟河由定</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l388' data-llen='10291:10314'>　陶至徐州入清河以逹江淮漕路又以吕梁灘磧之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l389' data-llen='10314:10337'>　險而罷至本朝始用之為運道云　潘季馴曰黄河</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l390' data-llen='10337:10360'>　自闗陜山西河南經豐碭出徐州接淮泗始為運道</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l391' data-llen='10360:10390'>　㑹泗沂之水蜿蜒而至清口<span class='krp-note'>在清河縣/名南河口</span>㑹淮而東運</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l392' data-llen='10390:10413'>　河自瓜儀至淮安則南資髙寳諸湖之水西資淮黄</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l393' data-llen='10413:10436'>　二河之水由清口至鎮口閘則資黄河與汶泗之水</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l394' data-llen='10436:10463'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0052', 'WYG', '004-22b' );" name="004-22b" class="pb">[004-22b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l395' data-llen='10463:10494'>　由鎮口閘至臨清則資汶泗之水<span class='krp-note'>即泰安萊蕪/徂崍諸泉</span>由臨清</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l396' data-llen='10494:10517'>　至天津則資汶河與漳衛之水由天津至都則資潞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l397' data-llen='10517:10542'>　白桑乾諸水<span class='krp-note'>濟寧而上資汶濟/寧而下兼資泗沂</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l398' data-llen='10542:10545'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l399' data-llen='10545:10548'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l400' data-llen='10548:10551'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l401' data-llen='10551:10554'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l402' data-llen='10554:10563'>　禹貢長箋卷四</span><br/>
